# nusex

[![PyPi version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/nusex.svg)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/nusex/)
[![PyPI - Status](https://img.shields.io/pypi/status/nusex)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/nusex/)
